    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a separate, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>gnocchi</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until crispy and starting to brown</p><p>Tip: Don’t stir too often as this will prevent the gnocchi from crisping!</p><p>Once browned and crispy set aside until later</p>",
