      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>garam masala </strong>and <strong>ground paprika </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>– this is your <strong>masala sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
