            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>smoked basa fillet[s]</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped basa </strong>to the<strong> masala sauce</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 4-5 min further or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
